Last night was intense. Chris, Chase, Russ and I all went to Paddy's (I haven't been there in like a year)and it was awesome. I went chasing after this girl that was in my french class in college because at that time I was in dire need of speaking French, and who do I stumble upon? None other than four classmates from high school. Ben Mey and his girlfriend, Josh Hammond, Ross Gavin, and Jeremy Chalut. They invited me back to Hammond's and we set off fire works, from China of course, really illegal apparently... it was a blast! The huge one fell over and we were running for our lives, one exploded at the house... and they were showing the house at noon today... and Ross put the first firework in the tube upside down so that one spread across the yard and totally blew up the tube... thankfully we had more than enough... two more sets... Somehow I made it home around 4:30... and I feel fantastic! I should have gotten sick from everything I mixed... First drink was of course a Car Bomb, it's a trademark for Paddy's, then the Polar Bears, 2 shots of Crown Royal, 2 of these raspberry shots, and a shot of some other kind of whiskey, I'm not sure how I'm still alive. At Josh's, I was sitting just sitting, and I realized that I am so glad to have the friends and the amazing boyfriend that I have. I admit, there are some things I dislike greatly, but once I was in a different enviorment then I am used to, I realized I wouldn't change mine for the world. Well, maybe the world, but that's it. 
Warped Tour is Saturday!! Nick is going to come with Sarah and I, first concert, and I think if he gets the chance, he'll try and rape the academy... haha. no, really. I'll have to warn them!

My emotions are toying with me today. Me heart leaves and feels broken, but then it suddenly returns and a smile is on my face. Perhaps I'm going insane. Crazy from what you do to me, and how much I love it. From the late nights to the early morning departures. It's not how it sounds. There's something more to this. 
I shall be posting more frequently, since this is a live journal, not a "I have departed from my natural state of being somewhat concious about the world and living in it to throw out little bits of my life" journal.
I have all intentions of being "well" not "good", for that is what was asked of me, what was wanted and proper. Yet why should I listen...
I miss your lips and your touch. I will be seeing you soon.
I'm right back. Learn to love me.

You Shall Never Know Who or Why I'm hiding... 


Unless I told you of course!
